WIPE OUT 
(C) GONZO GAMES 1990
South Bank Technopark, 90 London Rd, London, SE1 6LN (01-922 8856)

Welcome to the intergalactic hoverboard challenge. You're locked in an 
area against a hostile opponent. As you move around the area, you 
leave a crystalised wake behind you. So does your opponent. To win you 
must force your opponent to make a mistake. Contact with any wall is a 
big mistake. 

Simply plug in a joystick and go.

Up - forward fast
Up and fire - forward even faster if turbo option fitted to board
Fire - jump 
Left - slow left turn
Right - slow right turn
Diagonal left - fast left turn
Diagonal right - fast right turn


Please note the full game features countless opponents, two player 
option, different arenas and much more.
